#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.inner.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.inner"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inner.inner:1 of
msgid "Returns the inner product of a and b for arrays of floating point types."
msgstr "返回浮点类型数组 a 和 b 的内积。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.inner.inner:3 of
msgid ""
"Like the generic NumPy equivalent the product sum is over the last "
"dimension of a and b. The first argument is not conjugated."
msgstr ""
"与通用的 NumPy 等价函数类似，乘积和是对 a 和 b 的最后一个维度进行计算。"
"第一个参数不取共轭。"

